{"tid":2362207,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"三人被控去年元旦遊行期間刑毀滙豐及拒捕等 兩人罪名不成立 一人罪成還押候判","createTime":"2021-01-11T09:35:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-11T13:30:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b0f5660ab9d56c7b0130275606699c9141dfdd","tid":2362207,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T09:35:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12821\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F12821&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BZAoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=142d4f81\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/12821</a><br />\n<br />\n#東區裁判法院第十庭 <br />\n#張志偉裁判官 <br />\n#20200101灣仔 #審訊 #刑事損壞 #管有工具作非法用途 #拒捕<br />\n<br />\nD1:高(17)  <br />\nD2:黎(21)  <br />\nD3:梁(16)<br />\n<br />\n(1)刑事損壞 (D1,D2 ) <br />\n於本年1月1日，在香港灣仔軒尼詩道71號至85號的滙豐銀行分行之外，分別損壞屬分行的出入口之玻璃門及木圍板<br />\n<br />\n(2)管有適合作非法用途的工具及意圖作非法用途使用(D1)<br />\n於本年1月1日，在香港灣仔軒尼詩道71號至85號的滙豐銀行分行之外，管有1個爆破玻璃鎚，1支鉗和1個扳手(士巴拿)<br />\n<br />\n(3)抗拒在正當執行職務的警務人員(D2) <br />\n於本年1月1日，在香港灣仔軒尼詩道71號至85號的滙豐銀行分行之外，抗拒在正當執行職務的警長C<br />\n<br />\n(4)抗拒在正當執行職務的警務人員(D3)<br />\n被控於2020年1月1日，於灣仔軒尼詩道香港上海滙豐銀行外抗拒警長D<br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n基於裁判官參照《裁判官條例》第27條修改控罪，D2無需重新答辯。<br />\n<br />\n========<br />\n❗️速報❗️<br />\n<br />\n控罪1<br />\nD1 修訂控罪前的罪名不成立✅<br />\n（然，修改控罪下被刪去D1，亦沒有新控罪）<br />\nD2 罪名成立❗️<br />\n<br />\n控罪2<br />\nD1 罪名不成立✅<br />\n<br />\n控罪3 <br />\nD2 罪名成立❗️<br />\n<br />\n控罪4<br />\nD3 罪名不成立✅<br />\n<br />\n總結而言<br />\nD1全部罪名不成立，當庭釋放✅<br />\nD2全部罪名成立❗️<br />\nD3罪名不成立，當庭釋放✅<br />\n<br />\nD1有訟費申請，駁回申請❌<br />\n法庭將為D2索取背景報告及勞教報告，期間還押❗️<br />\n<br />\n押後至2021年1月25日1430東區裁判法院第十庭作判刑"},{"pid":"e3c4a77df40ba5f81aec3846c695a3cf18e27b09","tid":2362207,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:29:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec70d1022b279f865d41afd1af1a9df190fdf3b","tid":2362207,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57b2c67eddbd3d92887f4d75b8221d28c34063bc","tid":2362207,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec70d1022b279f865d41afd1af1a9df190fdf3b","tid":2362207,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1082fd02e37a46f06dde4f9e1dcabdbd34070cab","tid":2362207,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"57b2c67eddbd3d92887f4d75b8221d28c34063bc","tid":2362207,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fec70d1022b279f865d41afd1af1a9df190fdf3b","tid":2362207,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:31:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:32:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:33:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b3b6c21da9ca528b04ca5d18d59581285ce1f6d5","tid":2362207,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:39:58.000Z","msg":"點解D1冇事 D2有 有冇解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f683ab72399e66bc9f2031daa435ffd411f8a15a","tid":2362207,"uid":53498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:42:12.000Z","msg":"一個都嫌多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48b731b1ecd6309db865588b8b7c94752f81f495","tid":2362207,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:45:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0243cdae972a62795dc20af51aa154e5f845872","tid":2362207,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b3b6c21da9ca528b04ca5d18d59581285ce1f6d5","tid":2362207,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T10:39:58.000Z","msg":"點解D1冇事 D2有 有冇解釋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T11:57:24.000Z","msg":"去年民陣元旦大遊行當日，多區發生警民衝突，數百人被捕，其中三名男學生涉「裝修」滙豐銀行灣仔軒尼詩道分行，被控刑事毀壞及阻差辦公等四罪。案件經審訊後，裁判官裁定其中一人罪成，還柙候判；另兩名被告則因警員證人作供時迴避問題，被裁定罪名不成立，可全身而退。惟裁判官指，脫罪被告從黑衣人堆中走出，而一般人不會有膽量從黑衣人控制的地方行出來，認為被告自招嫌疑，拒批辯方訟費申請。<br />\n<br />\n案中三名被告依次是時為17歲姓高男生、21歲學生姓黎男生及16歲姓梁男生。高、黎兩人原被控於當天刑事損壞滙豐銀行的玻璃門及木圍板；高則涉管有適合作非法用途的工具罪。黎、梁兩人另被控一項抗拒正當執行職務警務人員罪。<br />\n<br />\n便衣探員供稱看到黎用噴漆在銀行木圍板上噴字，隨即上前裁停黎並表露身。張官指，便衣探員視線沒有被阻，作供堅定及毫不動搖，故裁定黎刑事損壞罪成；而黎明知對方是警員，被捕時掙扎導致對方受傷，故裁定黎抗拒正當執行職務警務人員罪成。張官將黎還柙至本月25日，其間索閱背景及勞教中心報告再判刑。<br />\n<br />\n至於梁，辯方立場指他當時不知便衣警長D是警員，才作出自衞行為；且當時現場嘈吵，梁根本聽不到警長D的說話。張官指，警長D庭上作供時，雖表明多次向梁表露警員身分，例如說「警察，咪郁」，但他並無在書面供詞提及此事。<br />\n<br />\n儘管警長D解釋表露身份是正常反應，惟張官認為正常反應與有否發生，可以是兩碼子的事；且警長D在盤問下態度迴避，而梁沒有案底，不排除他聽不到「警察，咪郁」，故裁定他罪脫。<br />\n<br />\n代表高的大狀一度提出訟費申請，指當時是合法遊行，高並非自招嫌疑。惟張官指一般人不會有膽量從黑衣人控制的地方行出來，認為高的行為自招嫌疑，拒批訟費申請。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210111/6OX7WWJ63ZFVPBJHXUXD4UNAGM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210111%2F6OX7WWJ63ZFVPBJHXUXD4UNAGM%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BZAoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=1ec5dac0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210111%2F6OX7WWJ63ZFVPBJHXUXD4UNAGM%2F&h=13dc5059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210111/6OX7WWJ63ZFVPBJHXUXD4UNAGM/</a>"},{"pid":"034e5cd7c26ef2a80c12511a3d5ee1b7eba2cb52","tid":2362207,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T12:58:08.000Z","msg":"辯方則在書面陳詞中多番質疑警長 C 是否可信、可靠，警長 C 承認從未見到手持噴漆男子的容貌，他更稱該男子被他制服時戴著黑色口罩，惟實際上次被告戴著淺藍色口罩。辯方又指，從閉路電視片段，辯方指出一名與警長 C 衣著吻合的人在提款機中心外往兩邊方向張望，指當時警長 C 視線已離開次被告。惟警長 C 則稱無法辨認出自己，並指「片段只係片面嘅一段」，指自己在鏡頭右移後看不到的地方截停次被告。<br />\n<br />\n裁判官不同意辯方所指，認為警長 C 清楚交代為何自己沒有出現在片段中，接納警長 C 有即時截停被告及警長 C 視線從未有離開過次被告的證供。裁判官續指，當被問及表明身分的時序，警長 C 在盤問時一直都回答當時動作十分連貫，事情發生在短時期內，「唔知邊個先邊個後」。裁判官同意警長說法，指他無法如「攝錄機般逐格逐格記落黎」，亦無須將具細無遺的細節放入證人供詞。他認為警長已如實交代事實，次被告黎柏璣亦必然知道警長 C 為警察，故裁定黎一項刑事毀壞及一項抗拒正在當執行職務的警務人員罪名成立。<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/ab-%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E4%B8%89%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90-22-%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%97%E6%8B%92%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E5%8F%A6%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2Fab-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2597%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590-22-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E5%258F%25A6%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&d=bDhD0m8o4fsrNJ%2BdslRS%2BZAoa2UDg2CF3RpsD8fDyZM%3D&h=d88e8691\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2Fab-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%2597%25A6%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E9%2581%258A%25E8%25A1%258C-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258C%2587-%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E6%25BB%2599%25E8%25B1%2590-22-%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E5%2588%2591%25E6%25AF%2580%25E5%258F%258A%25E6%258A%2597%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E6%2588%2590-%25E5%258F%25A6%25E4%25BA%258C%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%2584%25AB%25E7%25BD%25AA%2F&h=d7248212\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/court/ab-%E5%85%83%E6%97%A6%E5%A4%A7%E9%81%8A%E8%A1%8C-%E4%B8%89%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8C%87-%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E6%BB%99%E8%B1%90-22-%E6%AD%B2%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E5%88%91%E6%AF%80%E5%8F%8A%E6%8A%97%E6%8B%92%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E7%BD%AA%E6%88%90-%E5%8F%A6%E4%BA%8C%E4%BA%BA%E8%84%AB%E7%BD%AA/</a>"},{"pid":"88b20ed9db711459474c59bd6dab65acf288c8a5","tid":2362207,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-11T13:29:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfa0